OL,3,CCould Jersey and Guernsey now have two
OL,4,Cseparate ferry service providers?
OL,6,FIndustry leaders have weighed in on
OL,7,Fwhether separate ferry service
OL,8,Fproviders to Jersey and Guernsey could
OL,9,Fwork and what it would mean for
OL,10,Fcustomers.
OL,12,FIt comes after Guernsey named Brittany
OL,13,FFerries as their chosen provider for
OL,14,Fpassenger and freight sea services for
OL,15,Fthe island, while Jersey is yet to
OL,16,Fmake a decision.
