OL,3,CCould Jersey and Guernsey now have two
OL,4,Cseparate ferry service providers?
OL,6,FDeputy Kirsten Morel, the Minister for
OL,7,FSustainable Economic Diversity in
OL,8,FJersey, said: "I think it's really
OL,9,Fimportant that Jersey makes the right
OL,10,Fdecision, I wanted it to be for the
OL,11,FChannel Islands and in many ways I
OL,12,Fstill think it is about the Channel
OL,13,FIslands, but we need to make the right
OL,14,Fdecision for Jersey.
OL,16,F"We need to make sure that Jersey tax
OL,17,Fpayers aren't placed at risk in any
OL,18,Fway because the sustainability of the
OL,19,Fbidders isn't there for the 15 year
OL,20,Fperiod. We need more information from
OL,21,Fthese bidders.
