OL,6,F"I don't think both parties
OL,7,Fnecessarily felt like they needed more
OL,8,Finformation. We definitely did. Jersey
OL,9,Fonly gets one chance in every 15 years
OL,10,Fto do this contract, if we get it
OL,11,Fwrong, that's 15 years of difficulty
OL,12,Fpotentially and I want to avoid that."
OL,14,FWhen asked if both islands could
OL,15,Foperate a separate service, Steve
OL,16,FBailey, an ex Senior Manager for
OL,17,FCondor Ferries said: "Absolutely not,
OL,18,Fcategorically not. It would be to the
OL,19,Fdetriment of our services totally.
